    <div class="callout avoid-break"><strong style="color:#2f7d84;">STEP 3 &nbsp; Discussion and resolution</strong><br>You can book an appointment with Hendry Dai, and then you would be welcome to bring any support person that you wish to, and discuss about your complaint and possible solutions. We would be happy to arrange a mediator to attend a meeting if you wish. Hendry Dai will seek to give the final solution(s) to the complaint within 10 working days of meeting with you or receiving full details of it.</div>

    <p>If you remain dissatisfied with our response and consider that we have demonstrated negligence, incompetence, incapacity, or dishonest or misleading behaviour, or that we have breached the Licensed Immigration Advisers Code of Conduct, you may take your complaint to the Immigration Advisers Authority (the "Authority").</p>

